Otto Versand win German logistics award . German mail order company Otto Versand has won the 1996 German Logistics Award , the Germany shipper association ( BVL ) said . Otto Versand gained the BVL award for its successful 700 million marks five year re - design of its warehousing system which increased warehouse productivity by 27 percent , the BVL said . The company cut the time from when an order is processed to to delivery to 2 . 3 days from five days by more flexible delivery working times , introducing Germany - wide 24 - hours delivery services and opening two additional distribution centres . - Air Cargo Newsroom Tel + 44 171 542 7706 Fax + 44 171 542 5017 
